{"tid":796249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警長尋死】家庭問題偕妻上水家中企圖自殺　朋友上門及時救兩命","createTime":"2018-08-27T15:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T16:22:08.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb81b7e00fc064be93877bdd27db12eae6d657b5","tid":796249,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:56:05.000Z","msg":"新界北一名警長偕妻在家中尋死，幸好及時向朋友求助，友人上門，及時救回兩人，重案組接手調查。據了解，事發於今日（27日）凌晨1時許，新界北總區一名姓李的沙展，因家庭問題，與妻子在上水馬會道一單位內自殺，其間有人向朋友求助，朋友上門了解，及時發現及救回兩人。案件列作企圖自殺，交由大埔警區重案組第一隊跟進。據知，該名警長在2016年獲頒發香港警察長期服務獎章，因家庭問題感不開心，事件並不涉及錢債、感情等問題。"},{"pid":"6b71f5ecad671751446f8563afdd2f7c36dbc943","tid":796249,"uid":1333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"點解其他職業唔需要講明事件並不涉及錢債、感情等問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不涉及感情既家庭問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b96d612ca9bb6e223491deb6ffb5eb0a3a62024","tid":796249,"uid":10157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b71f5ecad671751446f8563afdd2f7c36dbc943","tid":796249,"uid":1333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"點解其他職業唔需要講明事件並不涉及錢債、感情等問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不涉及感情既家庭問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5bd840e389dccb252dfaa8ec64d65d50fdf2f3","tid":796249,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T16:08:10.000Z","msg":"多事"},{"pid":"05b9e9e7493757f344b17dc7f9bdc0dfd7fe5406","tid":796249,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b71f5ecad671751446f8563afdd2f7c36dbc943","tid":796249,"uid":1333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"點解其他職業唔需要講明事件並不涉及錢債、感情等問題<img sr